<P>

My special thanks go to Carol Digel (Wilmington, Delaware, USA) who has meticulously revised the proofs of these e-texts in their typos and punctuation errors.
<P>
These e-texts and their HTML documents are so devised that they can afford a proof of my own making. All rights are reserved. They are only for your private use. No part of them may be reproduced on the Internet or any other media without the permission of <A HREF="mailto:matsuoka@lang.nagoya-u.ac.jp">Mitsuharu Matsuoka</A>.
<P>
The Japanese code prevents you from viewing any accents on the Netscape browser. Netscape users are advised to select the Latin1 code or the ISO-8859. 

